1. Daily Report (individual tasks);
2. Weekly KPI Tracking Report;
3. Weekly Department Report (HR & Admin, IT and Property Management);
4. Monthly Performance Report (HR & Admin, IT and Property Management);
5. Semester Performance Report (HR & Admin, IT and Property Management);
6. Yearly Performance Report (HR & Admin, IT and Property Management);
7. Department Budgeting;
8. Headcount Planning, Recruitment Plan and Interview Schedule;

** Others
1. The Employee is strongly advised to follow the Company's Internal Rules and Regulations (HR Policy). In case of violation or breaching, the disciplinary measures will be applied as set forth by the levels of misconducts;
2. The Employee is strongly advised to be timely and punctual, respect hierarchy, work as a team, support, cooperate and communicate;
3. The Employee is strongly advised to give feedback and/or report about the status within appropriate timeframe when asked or assigned jobs;
4. The performance review period is once in 3 months by CEO and Board Members;
5. The work flow and communication line are duly stated in the detailed Sub-Structure of Operations Department;
6. This Job Description is nominated for the Employee to implement effectively for the date of its signatures;

